#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:9
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip[1]"
msgstr "A strange broadcast seems to be coming from this beacon."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:10
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip[2]"
msgstr "An unvisited location."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:12
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Upon arriving at the beacon, you come face to face with a bizarre broken "
"cruiser of Obelisk design. It bears colors and weapons that you haven't seen"
" before, not even in this dreadful place. The ship attempts to open "
"communication."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:15
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Approach the broken cruiser and try to receive the hail."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:17
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"From the ship's feed there blares a mix of static and what can barely be considered words in a short, 10-second loop. Not only does the signal distortion make the message a nightmare to decode, but the words appear to be a dialect of Obelisk speech too ancient for Aenwithe's translation algorithm to decode. You surmise that if you install a better translation package, you may be able to understand the message.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tYour scanners also detect the presence of crew inside the ship, though they seem to be fully automated and require no external input. They don't react at all to your direct hailing attempts."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:21
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Try to translate manually."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:23
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide to do it the hard way by performing extensive linguistic analysis"
" to learn an ancient Obelisk dialect. You spend a few days sitting in front "
"of the strange broken cruiser, enriching your translator."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:26
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:32
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Install the Runic Translator. [Cost: 10~, 1|]"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:34
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "You install the translator and wait to see what it can decode."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:42
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:48
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Runic Translator) We already have the translator; decode what the ship is "
"saying!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:50
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "You turn on your runic translator and wait to see what it can decode."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:52
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"UPG_AETHER_TRANSLATOR\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:58
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_DIRECTOR_DRONES_AND_DRONE_CONTROL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Director Drone) See if we can get our Director to translate the text for "
"us."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:60
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_DIRECTOR_DRONES_AND_DRONE_CONTROL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You feed the data into your Director and wait to see what it can decode."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:62
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_DIRECTOR_DRONES_AND_DRONE_CONTROL\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:68
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COMMONWEALTH_OBELISK\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Commonwealth Crew) Ask one of our Commonwealth Obelisks to translate the "
"weird language."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:70
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COMMONWEALTH_OBELISK\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Commonwealth Obelisk quickly writes up a full translation of the message"
" for you and your crew to read."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:72
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COMMONWEALTH_OBELISK\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:78
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_ANCIENT_NO_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Obelisk Crew) Your obelisks have no clue what language is being spoken."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:82
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COGNITIVE_NOT_METAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Cognitive Crew) Ask one of our non-Metal Cognitives to translate the weird "
"language."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:84
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COGNITIVE_NOT_METAL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Cognitive immediately sets to work decoding the message, with no sign of"
" difficulty."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:86
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"FR_BLUELIST_COGNITIVE_NOT_METAL\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:92
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "Dear lord, shut down the radio system and blow it up!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:94
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You power up your weapons, and the drone does the same. Even in its damaged "
"state, it's likely to put up quite a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:97
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:103
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/text"
msgstr "Leave this strange ship alone."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:105
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide that decoding the message isn't worth your time. You prepare to "
"jump instead."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:107
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:111
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:119
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"Attack that ship, whatever it is it should have something of use inside it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:121
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You power up your weapons, and the drone does the same. Even in its damaged "
"state, it's likely to put up quite a fight."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:124
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:130
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave the cruiser alone."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:132
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You have far more important problems to solve than handling a damaged "
"obelisk cruiser."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:134
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:138
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:146
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once the cacophonous message is fully translated, you discover the ship was "
"likely used as a mobile weapons factory in the Obelisk civil wars long ago. "
"Even in its damaged state, its ability to synthesize new equipment could "
"prove useful. Accessing the forge may prove difficult without shutting it "
"down first, however."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:148
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Attempt to hack the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:150
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You set up a program to attack the Auto-ship's AI module. If you want this "
"plan to work, you will have to hold out against the ship without destroying "
"it!"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:154
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[1]/event/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"Survive without destroying the broken cruiser, so the hack routine can run."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:160
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:166
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_CREW_COMMONWEALTH\"]/text"
msgstr "See if any of our Commonwealth crew can speed up the hacking process."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:168
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_CREW_COMMONWEALTH\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your Commonwealth crew was around at the height of these drones' usage so "
"it's still familiar with their systems. It manages to disable the Cruiser's "
"firewalls without much issue."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:170
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_LIST_CREW_COMMONWEALTH\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:176
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Advanced Hacking) Use your main hacking system to speed up the hacking "
"process."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:178
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your highly advanced hacking system is well-suited to the task, and the "
"drone submits without much resistance."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:180
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[@req=\"hacking\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:186
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "This is too risky; back away from the Cruiser."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:188
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Whatever secrets this ship holds are not relevant to the current mission. "
"You turn away, preparing to jump."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:190
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:194
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_FORGE_CRUISER_TRANSLATED\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:202
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Once the ship's firewall is broken, it's only a matter of time until you're able to bring the entire vessel under your command. The forge within is still intact, but you will likely only get a single piece of equipment out of it before the ship falls apart from the damage it sustained during your attack.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tYou also find some kind of strange cubical device while searching the factory. If it's broken, you might be able to repair it with a powerful repair drone. You also miraculously find blueprints for the ship, albeit missing many key features, including its forge. Nevertheless, even a damaged cruiser of this caliber of technology can be useful to the Federation."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:208
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Make a Commonwealth weapon or drone."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:214
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Scrap the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:216
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You decide to salvage the old Auto-ship, making do with the basic scrap "
"metal you can collect from it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:219
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:225
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/text"
msgstr "(Commonwealth's Body) Attempt to repair the corpse."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:227
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTHS_BODY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The damaged factory struggles to scan the crew. Eventually, it appears to bring it back to life... but only for a moment before the forge's internal software crashes. Whatever is needed to repair the corpse is beyond the factory's repair capabilities.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tStrangely, the Commonwealth's brief resurrection seemed to have triggered a reaction. A strange anomaly appears on your sensors with the same energy signatures as the brief pulse you noticed the Commonwealth give off just before it shut down. Perhaps the source of the anomaly could contain the answer to bringing the body back to life permanently?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:236
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_MANDER_BROKEN_DEVICE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Mender Drone) The device seems broken; our Mender drone should be able to "
"fix it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:238
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_REQUIREMENT_MANDER_BROKEN_DEVICE\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It takes a long time to repair the heavily damaged device, but eventually "
"your Mender is able to fully reconstruct it. Upon activation, you receive a "
"strange signal from a point in the sector where your sensors just identified"
" a massive energy spike. Whatever is there must be important."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:247
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL_OPENED_AND_NO_DAISY\"]/text"
msgstr "The device doesn't seem broken; try activating it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:249
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL_OPENED_AND_NO_DAISY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You touch the device and it suddenly springs to life. As it activates, you "
"receive a strange signal from a point in the sector where your sensors just "
"identified a massive energy spike. Whatever is there must be important."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:257
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL_OPENED_AND_DAISY\"]/text"
msgstr "The device doesn't seem broken; try activating it."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:259
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL_OPENED_AND_DAISY\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You touch the device and suddenly it springs to life. Upon activation, you receive a strange signal from a point in the sector where your sensors just identified a massive energy spike. Whatever is there must be important.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tThe device also triggers the nearby deactivated Obelisk to restore its systems! It comes back to life fully this time, although it seems to take a little while before it recovers from its stupor. It scans the room, immediately launching into a monologue upon noticing you.\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\"Oh gosh! Who are you? WHAT are you? You look so...strange and fleshy; are you a native to the lesser empires, perhaps? No matter, my proto-waystone has already debriefed me on the events of the past few days. You wish to visit the refuge, right? Well, far be it from me to stop another missguided soul into breaching that hellish place, but I suppouse the least I can do is tag along for the ride. Who knows, maybe I can convince someone there to actually leave their isolated little gardens.\"\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\tShe turns to you before heading inside your ship. \"Oh, I forgot to introduce myself. My name is Bellrennis, but you can call my Daisy. Now, let's get going!\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:268
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN\"]/choice[@req=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_PORTAL_OPENED_AND_DAISY\"]/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Daisy"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:276
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN_FORGE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You breach the forge's firewalls to get it to construct something for you."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:278
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_CRUISER_WIN_FORGE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Construct a Proto-Cognitive."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_obelisk.xml.append:284
msgid ""
